OL,3,CMan admits punching police officer in
OL,4,Cface in mosque riots
OL,6,FA man has admitted punching a police
OL,7,Fofficer in the face during violent
OL,8,Fprotests outside of a mosque.
OL,10,FDerek Drummond, 58, was part of a 300-
OL,11,Fstrong group who gathered outside
OL,12,FSouthport mosque as tensions rose
OL,13,Fafter three young girls were killed in
OL,14,Fa stabbing on Monday 29 July.
OL,16,FMore than 50 police officers were
OL,17,Finjured after stones and bottles were
OL,18,Fthrown, with cars set alight and
OL,19,Fdestroyed during the riots.
