OL,3,CMan admits punching police officer in
OL,4,Cface in mosque riots
OL,6,FJoshua Sanderson-Kirk, prosecuting,
OL,7,Ftold Liverpool Magistrates Court PC
OL,8,FThomas Ball was deployed to the mosque
OL,9,Fon St Luke's Road, on 30 July, where
OL,10,Fthe group arrived shouting "this is
OL,11,Four f****** country" and "scumbag
OL,12,Fb*****ds".
OL,14,FThe court heard officers had to
OL,15,Fwithdraw for fear of being overwhelmed.
