OL,3,CMan admits punching police officer in
OL,4,Cface in mosque riots
OL,6,FPC Ball stood to protect colleagues as
OL,7,Fthey tried to put on riot gear when
OL,8,FDrummond, of Pool Street, Southport,
OL,9,Fbecame violent, shouting "sh*thouses"
OL,10,Fand moved towards him, punching him in
OL,11,Fthe face, Mr Sanderson-Kirk said.
OL,13,FBricks were later thrown after a
OL,14,Fgarden wall was broken down, the court
OL,15,Fwas told.
OL,17,FShort clips of footage from a body-
OL,18,Fworn camera and the police helicopter
OL,19,Fwere shown to the court.
