OL,3,CMan admits punching police officer in
OL,4,Cface in mosque riots
OL,6,FDrummond indicated guilty pleas to
OL,7,Fviolent disorder and assault by
OL,8,Fbeating of an emergency worker.
OL,10,FNo application for bail was made and
OL,11,FDistrict Judge Timothy Boswell
OL,12,Fremanded Drummond in custody for
OL,13,Fsentencing at Liverpool Crown Court on
OL,14,F29 August.
OL,16,FTwo women sat at the back of the court
OL,17,Ffor the hearing, one was in tears and
OL,18,Fthe other blew Drummond a kiss as he
OL,19,Fleft.
